high_descs: Take a left go into the hallway and take a left into the office and go to the first desk.
Pick up the black mug on the desk.
Turn right leave the room and take a right into the kitchen and go to the sink.
Put the mug in the sink, rinse it off, and take it out.
Turn left to the center countertop.
Put the mug in the upper left corner of the countertop far from the Chopping block.
anns.task_desc: Put the rinsed mug on the countertop.

high_descs: Move back,turn left and again turn left towards the kitchen
Go to the study table and pick the mug placed over it.
Take the mug and turn right and go into the kitchen near the sink.
Open the tap in the sink and wash the mug.
Take the mug out from the countertop and turn around.
Place the mug on the countertop.
anns.task_desc: Bring the mug from the study room, wash it and place it on the countertop in the kitchen.

high_descs: Turn left and turn left and turn right move towards the desk.
Pick the mug from the desk.
Turn right and again turn right move towards the sink.
Turn left to place the mug on the sink, pick the mug from the sink.
Turn left and turn right move towards the countertop.
Place the mug on the countertop.
anns.task_desc: To place the mug on the countertop.
